Future possibilities

- Install a scalable icon under $(datadir)/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps

- Refresh contents on CTRL-R, if -file used.

- Word search, and highlight all matches, on CTRL-F.

- Jump to next (CTRL-N) and previous (CTRL-P) match.

- Command line options (e.g. -find WORD) to open the window with all
  occurrences of WORD highlighted, and place cursor at the first occurrence.


